# Transp. Code
## Title 6
### Chapter 201. Gen. Provisions & Admin.
##### § 201.756 — Local Government Sponsor Responsibilities

A local government sponsor that submits notice under Section 201.755 (Notice to Department) is responsible for preparing all materials for:

    (1) project scope determination;

    (2) environmental reports;

    (3) the environmental review document;

    (4) environmental permits and conditions;

    (5) coordination with resource agencies; and

    (6) public participation.

*Added by Acts 2011, 82nd Leg., R.S., Ch. 1345 (S.B.1420), Sec. 21(a), eff. September 1, 2011.*
